name: Polysquares
description:
Polyblocks is not revealed yet. Come back later or - hey - why not be a little adventurous and buy or sell an unrevealed NFT?!

Polyblocks is a collection of 3001 unique ERC20 NFTs stored on the Polygon blockchain. Every Polyblock is a unique combination of squares arranged in a 5x5 grid over a colored circle. Although each Polyblock is unique, some might be considered rarer because of circle color or number of blocks.
